WEBVTT

00:11.240 --> 00:12.110
What did you say?

00:12.110 --> 00:12.640
His...

00:13.110 --> 00:15.160
His Majesty passed away.

00:15.720 --> 00:17.120
His Majesty passed away?

00:17.270 --> 00:18.130
Your Highness,

00:18.390 --> 00:19.710
please go with me now.

00:19.760 --> 00:20.760
The palace is in chaos.

00:20.760 --> 00:22.960
If we don't leave now, it'll be too late!

00:26.260 --> 00:28.660
Sachets and trinkets!
Come and take a look!

00:45.150 --> 00:46.240
A few days ago, His Majesty

00:46.240 --> 00:47.880
gave me this token,

00:48.560 --> 00:50.710
saying that now Biantang is not at peace,

00:50.710 --> 00:52.620
and that if anything were to happen
in the palace,

00:52.620 --> 00:54.340
I was to take you away.

00:55.320 --> 00:56.320
I didn't understand

00:56.320 --> 00:57.750
what he meant at the time,

00:58.640 --> 00:59.970
but I didn't dare to ask.

01:00.750 --> 01:01.880
I never expected...

01:03.000 --> 01:04.349
Listen to me!

01:04.560 --> 01:06.490
You're not allowed to go anywhere!

01:06.760 --> 01:08.350
Just stay in the mansion.

01:08.680 --> 01:10.350
You, a deposed princess,

01:10.970 --> 01:13.150
and I, a useless prince,

01:13.710 --> 01:15.450
are a match made in heaven.

01:15.780 --> 01:17.640
I will achieve every single thing

01:17.640 --> 01:20.789
I promised you!

01:23.150 --> 01:25.120
If you don't want to get married yet,

01:25.120 --> 01:27.430
we can pretend
today's wedding never happened.

01:27.430 --> 01:28.890
I can keep waiting for you,

01:29.220 --> 01:30.980
until you fall in love with me,

01:31.550 --> 01:33.810
until the day
you truly want to be my wife.

01:34.420 --> 01:35.120
Chun'er!

01:35.870 --> 01:37.640
No matter what you've been through,

01:37.640 --> 01:39.070
I will not leave you.

01:39.509 --> 01:41.170
For all those who wronged you,

01:41.840 --> 01:44.479
I will make them pay double for you.

01:46.350 --> 01:49.080
Then can you temporarily
treat me as that person,

01:49.310 --> 01:50.789
until you truly forget him

01:51.350 --> 01:52.750
and are no longer in pain?

01:53.039 --> 01:54.500
As long as you are willing,

01:54.710 --> 01:56.310
I can always accompany you.

02:02.560 --> 02:03.350
Li Yan...

02:06.150 --> 02:07.790
You liar.

02:10.320 --> 02:13.050
What gives you the right
to make decisions for me?

02:14.400 --> 02:15.400
You said

02:16.310 --> 02:17.640
you would make anything

02:18.960 --> 02:20.870
you promised me happen.

02:22.630 --> 02:23.870
But what about now?

02:24.800 --> 02:26.750
Where are you now?

03:52.050 --> 03:57.340
[REBIRTH]

03:57.750 --> 04:00.290
[Episode 23]

04:08.910 --> 04:09.520
How is it?

04:09.630 --> 04:11.400
Any news of His Majesty
and the main force?

04:11.400 --> 04:12.260
Your Highness.

04:12.470 --> 04:15.080
The post road back to Great Yan
is just ahead at the foot of the mountain.

04:15.080 --> 04:16.680
But I asked the nearby villagers,

04:16.680 --> 04:19.339
and none of them
saw any troops passing through.

04:19.870 --> 04:21.269
However, on my way back,

04:21.550 --> 04:22.460
I found this.

04:27.480 --> 04:29.480
It was likely left behind by soldiers who,
like us,

04:29.480 --> 04:31.410
got separated from the main force.

04:32.600 --> 04:33.460
Your Highness.

04:34.310 --> 04:36.240
Our Great Yan has suffered
a crushing defeat,

04:36.240 --> 04:37.800
and the main force has been scattered.

04:37.800 --> 04:39.920
If you ask me,
searching further is pointless.

04:39.920 --> 04:40.850
What did you say?

04:41.040 --> 04:43.480
Something must have happened
to His Majesty and General Cheng.

04:43.480 --> 04:45.940
Otherwise,
they would have come back for us.

04:46.190 --> 04:47.050
Your Highness,

04:47.270 --> 04:49.070
we brothers don't want to go back.

04:49.070 --> 04:52.120
Over the years,
Great Yan has been at war with Great Yong,

04:52.120 --> 04:54.510
and all the men in my family
were conscripted

04:54.510 --> 04:55.830
and have long since died in battle.

04:55.830 --> 04:57.560
Even if I go back
to the Capital of Great Yan,

04:57.560 --> 04:59.420
there is no home left for me there.

04:59.560 --> 05:01.720
You might as well just let us go.

05:03.040 --> 05:03.900
Your Highness,

05:03.920 --> 05:04.920
I'm just like him.

05:05.070 --> 05:06.560
I'm the only one left in my family.

05:06.560 --> 05:08.030
Great Yan is already poor,

05:08.030 --> 05:09.360
and now the taxes are heavy.

05:09.360 --> 05:10.600
We want to leave Great Yan

05:10.600 --> 05:12.000
and find a more prosperous place.

05:12.000 --> 05:14.160
We heard Biantang is a good place.

05:16.310 --> 05:18.480
Yes, let us go.

05:24.390 --> 05:26.250
You are all soldiers of Great Yan!

05:26.390 --> 05:28.120
According to Great Yan's military law,

05:28.120 --> 05:30.070
leaving now would make you deserters!

05:30.070 --> 05:31.630
You know better than I do

05:31.630 --> 05:33.090
what deserters will face!

05:35.190 --> 05:37.600
The Black Eagle Army
is His Majesty's most trusted guard

05:37.600 --> 05:39.060
and the pride of Great Yan.

05:39.640 --> 05:41.570
Now that Great Yan is in distress,

05:41.680 --> 05:43.680
you're going to abandon your honor?

05:44.390 --> 05:46.360
The Black Eagle Army has shed blood
on battlefields for years,

05:46.360 --> 05:47.430
suffering countless casualties.

05:47.430 --> 05:48.510
What was it all for?

05:52.510 --> 05:53.390
If you return

05:54.159 --> 05:56.190
to the Capital of Great Yan with me now,

05:56.190 --> 05:57.240
you will be escorting the Princess Consort

05:57.240 --> 05:58.950
of Great Yan back for His Majesty.

05:58.950 --> 06:00.600
I promise you in the name of His Majesty

06:00.600 --> 06:01.800
and the Helian Tribe,

06:01.920 --> 06:04.520
you will not only get gold, silver,
and horses,

06:05.000 --> 06:06.730
but also the title of Centurion

06:06.830 --> 06:08.600
or even Chiliarch.

06:09.530 --> 06:11.750
I am willing to escort you
back to the Capital of Great Yan,

06:11.750 --> 06:12.510
even if it costs my life!

06:12.510 --> 06:13.950
I am willing to escort you,

06:13.950 --> 06:15.280
even if it costs my life!

06:38.830 --> 06:39.890
What are you doing?

06:40.900 --> 06:43.300
You promised us promotion and wealth,

06:43.480 --> 06:44.360
and it's true.

06:44.950 --> 06:48.360
But we were the ones who brought up
leaving in the first place.

06:48.360 --> 06:49.800
We're afraid you'll go back on your word

06:49.800 --> 06:52.159
and settle accounts with us later.

06:52.920 --> 06:54.720
So there are some things

06:55.290 --> 06:57.760
we want to make clear to you now.

06:57.950 --> 06:59.560
I am the Princess Consort of Great Yan.

06:59.560 --> 07:01.290
How could I break my word to you?

07:02.390 --> 07:03.780
Put down your weapons now,

07:03.780 --> 07:06.110
and I will act
as if nothing ever happened.

07:08.870 --> 07:10.400
How about we put it this way?

07:10.680 --> 07:12.340
In this desolate wilderness,

07:12.560 --> 07:14.920
if anything were to happen
to Consort Helian,

07:14.920 --> 07:17.360
then no one would know we are deserters.

07:17.800 --> 07:18.480
Instead,

07:18.950 --> 07:20.480
people might even think

07:20.680 --> 07:23.360
we died heroically at Longyin Pass.

07:23.510 --> 07:25.370
Don't come over! Don't come over!

07:44.430 --> 07:45.360
General Huan?

07:50.370 --> 07:50.850
You...

07:52.600 --> 07:53.390
Aren't you...

07:53.390 --> 07:54.800
Aren't I already dead?

07:57.830 --> 07:59.000
Take this to protect yourself.

07:59.000 --> 08:01.420
Be careful not to get stabbed
in the back by your own people.

08:01.420 --> 08:02.120
Wait.

08:02.360 --> 08:03.430
Why are you here?

08:03.470 --> 08:04.730
Does His Majesty know?

08:06.850 --> 08:08.390
I saved your life

08:08.390 --> 08:09.510
only because you are a woman.

08:09.510 --> 08:10.870
If you keep asking so many questions,

08:10.870 --> 08:12.510
I'll throw you back up that mountain.

08:12.510 --> 08:14.970
There are far more beasts
up there than here.

08:19.380 --> 08:19.850
You...

08:23.480 --> 08:24.430
Stop pretending.

08:24.430 --> 08:26.560
I'm not falling for your tricks on men.

08:44.750 --> 08:45.860
It's been so many days.

08:45.860 --> 08:47.220
Why is she still so weak?

08:49.610 --> 08:51.920
When the body is overworked,
the spleen is affected.

08:51.920 --> 08:53.790
Excessive thinking affects the heart.

08:53.790 --> 08:55.500
Vital energy gets trapped
and cannot circulate,

08:55.500 --> 08:57.330
causing blood and qi to gradually deplete.

08:57.330 --> 08:58.750
Stop rambling.

08:59.110 --> 09:00.030
Put it simply.

09:01.840 --> 09:02.670
Simply put,

09:02.670 --> 09:03.910
she has internal heat,

09:03.910 --> 09:04.750
and combined with fatigue

09:04.750 --> 09:06.200
and mental strain,
she is now feeling unwell.

09:06.200 --> 09:07.510
She is fine now.

09:07.510 --> 09:09.550
Just needs proper rest and recovery.

09:09.550 --> 09:10.600
Including today's medicine,

09:10.600 --> 09:11.440
there are 5 doses in total,

09:11.440 --> 09:12.480
and 2 visit fees.

09:13.320 --> 09:14.200
That's 10 coins.

09:14.200 --> 09:15.260
Are you robbing us?

09:15.550 --> 09:17.680
My prices are clearly marked and fair.

09:31.530 --> 09:32.510
What are you doing?

09:32.510 --> 09:33.790
Are you kidding me?

09:34.510 --> 09:35.120
What are you doing?

09:35.120 --> 09:36.360
What are you doing with this?

09:36.360 --> 09:37.290
What do you want?

09:38.270 --> 09:38.840
Here.

09:43.960 --> 09:45.890
It's freshly made and full measure.

09:45.890 --> 09:48.040
It usually sells for 10 coins in my shop.

09:48.040 --> 09:49.390
You... Come on.

09:49.510 --> 09:51.200
Why give a doctor

09:51.200 --> 09:52.270
a hammer?

09:52.270 --> 09:53.000
Besides,

09:53.000 --> 09:54.960
you're just a helper here.

09:54.960 --> 09:57.000
Your manager is away for a few days,

09:57.000 --> 09:57.840
and you think you can just
take it upon yourself

09:57.840 --> 09:59.600
to use goods from the shop as collateral?

09:59.600 --> 10:00.550
This scrap metal

10:00.800 --> 10:02.130
is worth 2 coins at most.

10:15.910 --> 10:17.840
What are you doing with that blade?

10:19.320 --> 10:20.270
Don't mess with me.

10:20.270 --> 10:22.130
It's not worth risking your life.

10:22.910 --> 10:23.720
Here.

10:23.720 --> 10:25.980
This blade can sell for at least 10 coins.

10:26.120 --> 10:27.050
Keep the change.

10:27.590 --> 10:28.710
I'm not a butcher.

10:29.240 --> 10:30.440
Why give me a blade?

10:30.870 --> 10:31.630
No.

10:31.910 --> 10:33.630
You can't be a penny short.

10:37.360 --> 10:38.440
Are you taking advantage of us?

10:38.440 --> 10:38.840
Easy! Easy!

10:38.840 --> 10:39.840
You may break it!

10:41.370 --> 10:42.200
General Huan.

10:55.960 --> 10:57.560
This hairpiece is pure gold.

10:57.710 --> 11:00.440
It's worth a hundred times
the consultation fee.

11:05.200 --> 11:06.730
Hearing you speak just now,

11:07.120 --> 11:09.200
you're an old physician in this town.

11:09.360 --> 11:11.090
Huan Huan and I are old friends.

11:11.360 --> 11:13.440
I've been recuperating here these days.

11:13.440 --> 11:15.240
If there's anything wrong with this gold,

11:15.240 --> 11:17.000
just come back to me.

11:24.550 --> 11:27.630
Fine, I'll trust you this time.

11:30.660 --> 11:31.380
Goodbye.

11:32.650 --> 11:35.250
You tigress. She-devil.

11:35.550 --> 11:36.310
Witch.

11:37.150 --> 11:37.630
She-

11:41.130 --> 11:42.530
Thank you, General Huan.

12:36.870 --> 12:37.660
You're back?

12:37.910 --> 12:40.440
This is the stone-pot chicken
of Great Yan that I specially made.

12:40.440 --> 12:41.870
You've been away from the Capital
for so long.

12:41.870 --> 12:43.790
You must not have had it in a long time.

12:43.790 --> 12:44.440
And this.

12:44.540 --> 12:46.750
These are horse milk cakes
unique to the Helian Tribe.

12:46.750 --> 12:48.440
I went to several pastry shops in town

12:48.440 --> 12:49.520
before I finally found them.

12:49.520 --> 12:50.330
Try some and see

12:50.330 --> 12:53.590
if it tastes the same
as the ones in the Capital of Great Yan.

12:59.240 --> 13:00.240
General Huan,

13:00.870 --> 13:02.400
stop pretending to be cold.

13:02.720 --> 13:03.600
It's tiring.

13:08.440 --> 13:10.370
I saw your place was rather simple,

13:10.550 --> 13:12.150
so I brought you some things.

13:13.030 --> 13:13.970
I walked a long way

13:13.970 --> 13:15.760
to buy this quilt for the bed.

13:19.970 --> 13:20.900
And this heater.

13:21.190 --> 13:22.260
The weather here seems even colder

13:22.260 --> 13:24.060
than in the Capital of Great Yan.

13:25.830 --> 13:27.160
And these wildflowers.

13:31.160 --> 13:34.000
A woman should look like a woman.

13:38.130 --> 13:38.730
Let's eat.

13:59.550 --> 14:00.550
Hand me your bowl.

14:06.360 --> 14:07.820
You sold all your jewelry?

14:09.870 --> 14:11.550
Those are just worldly possessions.

14:11.550 --> 14:13.950
There are plenty
in the palace of Great Yan.

14:13.960 --> 14:15.560
I still have some money left.

14:15.600 --> 14:17.130
Keep it for your future use.

14:20.840 --> 14:21.320
Tell me.

14:21.870 --> 14:22.810
What do you want?

14:29.320 --> 14:30.850
I want to borrow your horse.

14:31.080 --> 14:32.510
I heard in the town

14:32.790 --> 14:35.870
that Yan Xun has returned safely
to the Capital of Great Yan.

14:35.870 --> 14:37.000
I should go back too.

14:40.000 --> 14:42.000
I know His Majesty has failed you

14:42.320 --> 14:43.850
and the Snowy Region Tribe.

14:44.320 --> 14:44.870
But...

14:45.750 --> 14:48.480
Great Yan
is now at a critical moment of survival.

14:48.840 --> 14:50.700
I must go back to help His Majesty.

14:51.840 --> 14:54.080
The Snowy Region Tribe has been loyal
to Great Yan for generations.

14:54.080 --> 14:55.080
General Huan, you...

14:55.080 --> 14:55.790
Say no more.

14:59.270 --> 15:00.070
General Huan!

15:00.870 --> 15:01.670
General Huan!

15:02.440 --> 15:03.240
General Huan!

15:04.840 --> 15:05.200
General Huan!

15:05.200 --> 15:05.870
That horse was originally

15:05.870 --> 15:08.000
a wild horse from the Huolei Plains
of Great Yan.

15:08.000 --> 15:09.800
It probably wants to go back too.

15:10.280 --> 15:11.230
Take it with you.

15:53.150 --> 15:54.320
[General Xiuli's Mansion]

15:55.870 --> 15:58.130
His Majesty told me before he passed away

15:58.240 --> 16:00.100
that he had an agreement with you.

16:01.000 --> 16:01.910
Once you and General Chu

16:01.910 --> 16:03.550
returned victorious from battle,

16:03.550 --> 16:05.680
he would lend you 500 imperial guards.

16:06.270 --> 16:06.790
Now,

16:07.150 --> 16:09.480
these 500 guards are all under my command.

16:10.390 --> 16:11.270
I am to

16:12.360 --> 16:13.820
hand this token over to you

16:14.120 --> 16:15.520
on His Majesty's behalf.

16:17.270 --> 16:20.800
It can be considered the fulfillment
of His Majesty's promise.

16:30.320 --> 16:30.960
Thank you.

16:32.110 --> 16:33.570
When I return from Ximeng,

16:33.960 --> 16:35.360
I will return them to you.

16:40.440 --> 16:41.240
Young master,

16:41.240 --> 16:43.030
everything we need to bring is here.

16:43.030 --> 16:44.000
I've packed winter quilts

16:44.000 --> 16:45.800
and coats made of sheepskin and deerskin,

16:45.800 --> 16:47.550
enough to keep us warm in Ximeng.

16:47.550 --> 16:49.480
There's also a chest
of gold and silver utensils,

16:49.480 --> 16:51.880
which can be sold for money
if needed later.

16:51.910 --> 16:53.480
Along with a box of Xiao Ran's medicine

16:53.480 --> 16:55.550
and Lady Chu's and Minglu's luggage,

16:56.470 --> 16:58.640
these two carriages should be enough.

16:59.320 --> 16:59.840
Okay.

17:01.500 --> 17:02.790
We're going to Ximeng

17:02.810 --> 17:05.069
to get the antidote for your young master,

17:05.069 --> 17:06.550
not to settle down.

17:07.170 --> 17:07.970
If you ask me,

17:08.230 --> 17:10.030
we should bring all the hidden weapons

17:10.030 --> 17:11.069
from Qingshan Manor.

17:11.069 --> 17:12.960
Needles, poisons—

17:13.069 --> 17:13.880
everything.

17:13.880 --> 17:15.349
Yes, you're right.

17:16.000 --> 17:17.310
Why didn't I think of that?

17:17.310 --> 17:17.960
Shiyi.

17:18.599 --> 17:19.069
There's no need.

17:19.069 --> 17:19.720
Master,

17:20.030 --> 17:21.400
have you seen Lady Chu?

17:21.400 --> 17:22.550
I went to her room this morning,

17:22.550 --> 17:23.750
and she wasn't there.

17:24.480 --> 17:25.720
When I was feeding the horses
this morning,

17:25.720 --> 17:27.400
I saw Lady Chu leaving in a carriage.

17:27.400 --> 17:29.400
She said she was going to the palace.

17:36.200 --> 17:36.930
What's this?

17:38.920 --> 17:41.550
This was left by His Majesty
before he passed away.

17:41.550 --> 17:42.280
At that time,

17:43.200 --> 17:45.310
the news of Biantang
defeating Great Yan's Black Eagle Army

17:45.310 --> 17:46.310
had just arrived.

17:47.480 --> 17:48.410
His Majesty said

17:49.240 --> 17:50.070
he wanted to grant you a title

17:50.070 --> 17:52.200
more impressive than mine and Li Qi's.

17:52.350 --> 17:53.880
But he never decided on one.

18:19.680 --> 18:21.000
Why is this here?

18:21.550 --> 18:23.310
His Majesty
had been on the throne for months

18:23.310 --> 18:25.040
but never established a harem.

18:25.310 --> 18:26.920
The Court of Rites
has advised him many times,

18:26.920 --> 18:28.180
but he never approved.

18:28.510 --> 18:31.640
Actually, His Majesty
wanted to wait for you to come back

18:32.150 --> 18:34.480
and express his feelings to you in person.

18:34.750 --> 18:36.310
He said that if you agreed,

18:36.680 --> 18:37.680
this decree

18:37.680 --> 18:39.680
would name you Empress of Biantang.

18:40.310 --> 18:40.880
But...

18:41.680 --> 18:43.740
he said you probably wouldn't agree.

18:43.920 --> 18:44.750
So most likely,

18:44.750 --> 18:46.880
he would just make you a great general,

18:47.030 --> 18:48.640
and send you off in glory

18:49.440 --> 18:51.590
to marry the man you love.

18:55.400 --> 18:58.260
A country cannot be without a ruler
for a single day.

18:58.350 --> 19:00.040
Biantang has just emerged from war,

19:00.040 --> 19:01.270
and the court is still unstable.

19:01.270 --> 19:03.110
This is a turbulent time.

19:03.310 --> 19:06.350
Since Emperor Ruili had no other heirs

19:06.440 --> 19:07.900
besides the late emperor,

19:07.960 --> 19:10.270
we should select a virtuous
and capable prince

19:10.270 --> 19:12.440
of the same generation
from the imperial clan

19:12.440 --> 19:14.790
to succeed the throne immediately

19:14.790 --> 19:15.680
and restore peace to the realm.

19:15.680 --> 19:17.270
That being said,

19:17.960 --> 19:20.000
this concerns the throne after all.

19:20.110 --> 19:24.030
Which prince within the royal clan
would be suitable?

19:24.240 --> 19:24.960
Well...

19:25.640 --> 19:27.070
What about Prince of Jing?

19:27.070 --> 19:29.920
He is Emperor Ruili's blood brother,

19:30.480 --> 19:32.590
so his accession to the throne
would be legitimate.

19:32.590 --> 19:34.320
That would not be appropriate.

19:34.640 --> 19:37.030
Although Prince of Jing is in his prime,

19:37.510 --> 19:39.510
he was born with a weak constitution

19:39.640 --> 19:41.440
and has always relied on medicine.

19:41.440 --> 19:43.830
He cannot even do
basic riding and archery.

19:43.830 --> 19:46.480
How could he bear the responsibility
of ruling a nation?

19:46.480 --> 19:47.510
In my view,

19:47.510 --> 19:49.110
it would be better
to recommend Prince of An.

19:49.110 --> 19:51.110
Prince of An
comes from a military background

19:51.110 --> 19:52.680
and has military achievements.

19:52.680 --> 19:54.070
His accession would win public support.

19:54.070 --> 19:55.800
That would not be appropriate!

19:56.510 --> 19:59.600
Prince of An has close ties with
the Zhou family of the southern region,

19:59.600 --> 20:01.920
and his wife is from that family.

20:02.290 --> 20:04.110
Lord He, have you forgotten the lesson

20:04.110 --> 20:07.840
from the chaos of the previous dynasty
caused by powerful in-laws?

20:10.550 --> 20:12.030
Chancellor,

20:12.240 --> 20:13.750
General Xiuli,

20:13.920 --> 20:16.250
and Left General of Cavalry have arrived!

20:23.160 --> 20:25.560
It's the late emperor's son, Prince Xiuyi.

20:27.880 --> 20:30.790
Prince Xiuyi is the late emperor's son.

20:31.070 --> 20:32.880
Since the late emperor has passed away,

20:32.880 --> 20:35.160
it is only natural that his only child
should ascend the throne.

20:35.160 --> 20:37.920
Although Prince Xiuyi
is the late emperor's son,

20:37.920 --> 20:39.960
his mother, Zhan Ziming,

20:39.960 --> 20:42.440
is the sister
of the convicted official Zhan Ziyu.

20:42.440 --> 20:43.850
The late emperor was kind

20:44.070 --> 20:46.720
and spared her
only because she was pregnant.

20:46.720 --> 20:49.880
How can he now be considered
a candidate for the throne?

20:49.880 --> 20:52.790
Moreover, Prince Xiuyi
is not even one year old.

20:53.030 --> 20:54.440
He is still an infant,

20:54.550 --> 20:57.350
unable to speak or walk.

20:57.920 --> 21:00.310
How could he possibly
sit firmly on the throne?

21:00.310 --> 21:02.160
A weak ruler ruling a strong state

21:02.160 --> 21:04.750
is a sign of impending chaos
in the nation.

21:04.750 --> 21:05.480
Indeed.

21:06.240 --> 21:08.170
Grand Secretary Liu, General Sun.

21:08.270 --> 21:09.640
This concerns the throne.

21:09.640 --> 21:11.110
You two must...

21:21.350 --> 21:23.680
Here's the late emperor's
posthumous edict!

21:23.680 --> 21:25.480
This edict...

21:25.640 --> 21:27.830
General Xiuli, Chu Qiao,

21:28.160 --> 21:29.920
is hereby granted
the title of Consort Xiuli.

21:29.920 --> 21:32.320
If she gives birth
to a prince in the future,

21:32.400 --> 21:35.030
she will be named Empress of Biantang.

21:35.160 --> 21:37.070
Now that the late emperor has passed away

21:37.070 --> 21:38.160
and the prince is still young,

21:38.160 --> 21:41.030
for the sake of Biantang's future,
the Consort

21:41.160 --> 21:44.310
has decided to adopt Prince Xiuyi.

21:44.550 --> 21:46.440
With his mother's noble status,

21:47.110 --> 21:49.310
why can't Prince Xiuyi take the throne?

21:53.750 --> 21:54.750
The edict is here.

21:55.160 --> 21:56.360
If anyone has doubts,

21:56.790 --> 21:58.320
you may come and take a look.

22:05.440 --> 22:07.920
Is this really the late emperor's edict?

22:10.310 --> 22:11.040
General Chu,

22:11.400 --> 22:13.110
are you sure you want to do this?

22:13.110 --> 22:15.910
I just need to complete
the imperial edict, right?

22:16.070 --> 22:18.270
There are no errors
in the signature and date.

22:18.270 --> 22:20.800
With you, Lord Sun and Lord Liu,
as witnesses,

22:21.000 --> 22:23.930
I believe the ministers
will not dare to question it.

22:30.720 --> 22:32.720
Since I have adopted Xiuyi as my son,

22:33.310 --> 22:34.910
I am considered to have a son.

22:35.200 --> 22:36.960
According to the late emperor's edict,

22:36.960 --> 22:39.620
I can be conferred
the title of Empress Dowager.

22:40.310 --> 22:41.510
My son is still young,

22:42.480 --> 22:44.740
so the Empress Dowager can act as regent.

22:44.750 --> 22:47.480
You are all pillars of the state.

22:47.720 --> 22:49.310
Can you devise plans for Biantang

22:49.310 --> 22:50.640
and its people,

22:51.270 --> 22:53.240
and help the late emperor's infant son

22:53.240 --> 22:54.680
secure this empire?

22:57.030 --> 22:59.400
Empress Dowager,
you are making plans for the sake of

22:59.400 --> 23:01.200
the late emperor and the people.

23:03.550 --> 23:05.400
We second the motion.

23:05.960 --> 23:07.920
We second the motion.

23:09.200 --> 23:10.600
Let me tell you the truth.

23:10.640 --> 23:11.880
You've been set up by us.

23:11.880 --> 23:13.480
We were sure that after seeing the edict,

23:13.480 --> 23:15.510
you would definitely stay
for the little prince.

23:15.510 --> 23:16.830
If you regret it now...

23:17.110 --> 23:18.160
The edict has been issued.

23:18.160 --> 23:19.960
How can this be treated as a game?

23:21.720 --> 23:24.000
As for the enthronement ceremony,

23:24.440 --> 23:26.900
we will need your help,
Grand Secretary Liu.

23:27.510 --> 23:29.770
Three days from now is an auspicious day.

23:29.830 --> 23:31.720
I will urge the Ministry of Rites
and the Ministry of Works

23:31.720 --> 23:33.350
to prepare everything
as quickly as possible.

23:33.350 --> 23:34.000
Thank you.

23:40.880 --> 23:42.550
This was all your bad idea.

23:43.830 --> 23:45.630
Miss Chu really is unfortunate.

23:46.030 --> 23:48.480
Biantang is now hanging by a thread.

23:48.720 --> 23:52.350
If chaos rises again, everyone
will suffer when the country falls.

23:52.350 --> 23:55.010
Do you think only the common people
will suffer?

23:55.030 --> 23:56.160
You, me,

23:56.830 --> 23:58.000
and Miss Chu—

23:58.920 --> 24:00.440
aren't we all part of it?

24:02.950 --> 24:05.120
[The border
between Great Yan and Great Yong]

24:11.640 --> 24:12.500
Your Highness!

24:12.590 --> 24:14.160
Why can't you keep your composure?

24:14.160 --> 24:15.020
Your Highness.

24:15.160 --> 24:17.560
Only you
can still keep your composure now.

24:19.790 --> 24:22.310
Our mission of supporting Biantang
this time

24:22.310 --> 24:23.440
has indeed been exhausting.

24:23.440 --> 24:24.310
In a few days,

24:24.920 --> 24:26.350
we will be able to return to camp to rest.

24:26.350 --> 24:27.210
Your Highness,

24:27.400 --> 24:28.830
we are not afraid of hardship.

24:28.830 --> 24:29.880
It was us who submitted
the military report

24:29.880 --> 24:30.920
to His Majesty this time.

24:30.920 --> 24:32.200
It hasn't yet reached Zhenhuangcheng,

24:32.200 --> 24:34.030
and the Thirteenth Prince has already
submitted a memorial against us.

24:34.030 --> 24:35.030
The charge is extremely serious,

24:35.030 --> 24:39.760
accusing us of unauthorized troop deployment
and harboring treasonous ambitions.

24:40.720 --> 24:43.440
We supported Biantang this time,

24:43.440 --> 24:45.100
severely defeated Great Yan,

24:45.830 --> 24:49.030
and resolved the crisis
between Great Yong and Great Yan.

24:49.160 --> 24:50.160
My father is wise.

24:50.400 --> 24:51.680
He will surely understand.

24:51.680 --> 24:52.540
Your Highness.

24:52.750 --> 24:53.590
In my opinion,

24:53.590 --> 24:54.750
just to be on the safe side,

24:54.750 --> 24:56.350
you should personally write a memorial
to explain the reasons.

24:56.350 --> 24:57.680
I will send an urgent courier

24:57.680 --> 24:58.640
to deliver it back to Zhenhuangcheng,

24:58.640 --> 24:59.480
just in case.

25:01.070 --> 25:01.640
No need.

25:02.440 --> 25:03.570
Report truthfully.

25:03.720 --> 25:05.440
If Father really wants to blame me,

25:05.440 --> 25:08.000
what's the use
of me petitioning personally?

25:08.170 --> 25:10.280
His Majesty is so partial
to the Thirteenth Prince.

25:10.280 --> 25:11.810
It is truly unfair to you.

25:12.400 --> 25:13.660
Is that something you should say?

25:13.660 --> 25:15.190
I just feel wronged for you.

25:15.440 --> 25:17.350
For years,
you have been guarding the border,

25:17.350 --> 25:18.510
risking your life for Great Yong.

25:18.510 --> 25:19.400
In the end, you were suppressed

25:19.400 --> 25:20.720
by a wet-behind-the-ears brat.

25:20.720 --> 25:21.200
Enough!

25:22.070 --> 25:22.830
Forgive me.

25:26.790 --> 25:28.250
Guards, prepare my horse.

25:30.310 --> 25:31.240
A bowl of noodles, please.

25:31.240 --> 25:32.960
Would you like to try our signature

25:32.960 --> 25:33.820
roast lamb leg?

25:34.000 --> 25:34.720
No, thanks.

25:38.550 --> 25:39.310
Sir, sir.

25:39.960 --> 25:41.960
You must have come from afar, right?

25:42.000 --> 25:43.310
Come, have a seat.

25:48.000 --> 25:49.400
Please come inside, sir.

25:49.880 --> 25:50.680
Please, sit.

25:51.200 --> 25:52.880
Sir, what would you like to eat?

25:52.880 --> 25:54.640
A bowl of noodles, a side dish,

25:54.960 --> 25:55.720
and a pot of wine.

25:55.720 --> 25:57.650
Would you like to try our signature

25:57.680 --> 25:58.830
roast lamb leg?

25:59.550 --> 26:00.110
Okay.

26:01.200 --> 26:02.130
Coming right up.

26:05.550 --> 26:06.510
Sir, your wine.

26:08.270 --> 26:10.330
The noodles will be ready in a moment.

26:10.510 --> 26:11.570
Sir, your noodles.

26:12.830 --> 26:14.290
Delicious roast lamb leg.

26:15.400 --> 26:17.480
Everything is first come, first served.

26:17.480 --> 26:19.030
Why did you serve him first?

26:20.400 --> 26:21.330
Enjoy your meal.

26:31.510 --> 26:33.110
Why are you so unreasonable?

26:35.240 --> 26:35.840
Forget it.

26:36.270 --> 26:37.070
Give it to her.

26:38.400 --> 26:39.600
Two more pots of wine.

26:40.070 --> 26:40.790
Hurry.

26:40.920 --> 26:42.750
Warm up two pots of wine
for the gentleman.

26:42.750 --> 26:43.920
Sir, you obviously look like

26:43.920 --> 26:46.480
a generous and blessed man.

26:46.750 --> 26:48.510
Not like some poor beggars.

26:48.960 --> 26:50.960
They may have little money,
but they're very demanding.

26:50.960 --> 26:51.890
Enjoy your meal.

26:55.070 --> 26:56.270
Don't mind him, miss.

26:56.350 --> 26:57.680
These noodles are on me.

26:58.270 --> 26:59.730
I am just passing through.

26:59.920 --> 27:02.720
May I ask if you are from this town?

27:40.550 --> 27:41.160
Miss,

27:41.450 --> 27:42.820
have you seen my purse?

27:42.850 --> 27:44.630
Two suspicious-looking beggars

27:44.630 --> 27:45.950
just passed by you.

27:46.480 --> 27:47.480
It was probably stolen.

27:47.480 --> 27:48.410
Since you saw it,

27:48.790 --> 27:50.110
why did you let them go?

27:50.310 --> 27:52.550
In a little shop
in the middle of nowhere like this,

27:52.550 --> 27:54.070
dressing so flashily makes you

27:54.070 --> 27:55.440
an easy target.

27:55.550 --> 27:56.920
Who else would they steal from?

27:56.920 --> 27:58.350
I'll pay for my own noodles.

27:58.350 --> 27:59.610
You don't need to do it.

28:19.550 --> 28:20.160
Miss!

28:28.510 --> 28:29.200
My horse?

28:44.200 --> 28:45.440
Why are you following me?

28:45.440 --> 28:46.570
I have a favor to ask.

28:49.510 --> 28:50.880
The thieves in the tavern

28:50.880 --> 28:52.160
not only stole my purse,

28:52.160 --> 28:53.160
but also my horse.

28:53.400 --> 28:55.800
My companions are waiting for me
30 li away.

28:55.920 --> 28:57.220
I can't afford to waste time.

28:57.220 --> 28:59.590
So I'd like to ask you to lend me a horse.

28:59.750 --> 29:01.680
Why does everyone
want to borrow a horse from me?

29:01.680 --> 29:02.740
Once I return home,

29:02.980 --> 29:04.910
I will repay you 10 times the price.

29:07.830 --> 29:08.490
Not enough?

29:09.800 --> 29:12.060
You can take advantage of the situation.

29:12.510 --> 29:13.480
Take advantage?

29:17.350 --> 29:18.610
You're a step too late.

29:18.710 --> 29:20.710
My horse has already been borrowed.

29:21.270 --> 29:24.110
Now all I have left
is this donkey used for milling.

29:37.400 --> 29:39.400
I really can't help you.

29:39.880 --> 29:41.610
You'd better find another way.

29:41.630 --> 29:42.110
Miss...

30:04.050 --> 30:06.840
[I will repay your kindness
for lending me the donkey.]

30:05.590 --> 30:06.920
Repay?

30:26.720 --> 30:27.750
I think it'd be great for General Chu

30:27.750 --> 30:29.350
to stay in Biantang.

30:29.480 --> 30:30.960
She will definitely meet a gentleman
from Biantang in the future

30:30.960 --> 30:33.590
who is more handsome, more skilled

30:33.590 --> 30:35.310
and loves her more than you do.

30:35.340 --> 30:36.720
He will fall for her, move her,

30:36.720 --> 30:37.830
and then marry her.

30:38.640 --> 30:40.750
From then on, she can live

30:40.750 --> 30:43.000
a happy and fulfilling life in Biantang.

30:43.000 --> 30:44.030
Then you can go back to Great Yong

30:44.030 --> 30:45.960
and keep being Young Master Zhuge.

30:53.160 --> 30:53.640
Wait.

30:54.200 --> 30:55.480
There is another possibility.

30:55.480 --> 30:57.680
You can stay in Biantang
until the poison flares up.

30:57.680 --> 30:58.350
Once you're dead,

30:58.350 --> 31:00.310
you'll become someone irreplaceable
in her heart,

31:00.310 --> 31:02.440
and she'll remember you
for the rest of her life.

31:02.440 --> 31:03.370
You are a doctor.

31:04.310 --> 31:06.480
Doctors rely on observation, auscultation,
inquiry, and palpation,

31:06.480 --> 31:07.880
not on nagging.

31:10.200 --> 31:11.060
Let me tell you.

31:11.200 --> 31:12.750
You refuse to tell General Chu
about your condition

31:12.750 --> 31:14.110
and have delayed here for so long.

31:14.110 --> 31:15.310
When the poison enters your heart,

31:15.310 --> 31:16.230
even if I get the antidote from Ximeng,

31:16.230 --> 31:17.270
I won't be able to save you.

31:17.270 --> 31:18.200
Then you can just wait for me

31:18.200 --> 31:19.860
to use your body for research.

31:23.220 --> 31:24.070
Help!

31:29.510 --> 31:30.370
What happened?

31:30.550 --> 31:31.390
Young Master Zhuge,

31:31.390 --> 31:32.450
who is this person?

31:35.790 --> 31:36.920
He said he was looking for you

31:36.920 --> 31:38.320
and then collapsed here.

31:46.440 --> 31:47.570
He is badly injured.

31:47.570 --> 31:48.750
It's probably from torture.

31:48.750 --> 31:49.770
I have given him medicine,

31:49.770 --> 31:51.770
but I don't know when he will wake up.

31:53.200 --> 31:55.800
This piece of leather
was found in his clothes.

32:00.350 --> 32:02.200
This belongs to the Queen of Lingyue.

32:02.200 --> 32:03.660
She is in danger in Ximeng.

32:03.770 --> 32:04.400
You mean...

32:04.400 --> 32:06.240
The Ximeng delegation
had an accident in Biantang,

32:06.240 --> 32:08.900
and only the Queen of Lingyue
and Baze returned.

32:10.000 --> 32:12.750
King Ximeng might not easily let them go.

32:17.350 --> 32:18.150
Young Master,

32:18.270 --> 32:19.310
Miss Chu is back.

32:21.030 --> 32:21.710
Got it.

32:22.200 --> 32:23.000
Young Master,

32:23.310 --> 32:24.350
Miss Chu...

32:52.590 --> 32:53.240
Young Master,

32:53.240 --> 32:55.170
you must not let Miss Chu stay here.

32:55.590 --> 32:56.990
Even if not for yourself,

32:57.030 --> 32:58.030
think of her.

32:58.830 --> 33:01.030
How many times
have you faced death together

33:01.030 --> 33:02.400
to get to this point?

33:15.790 --> 33:17.450
Young Master, say something.

33:17.550 --> 33:19.010
Ask Miss Chu to go with you.

33:23.590 --> 33:26.440
I will stay in Tangjing
for a few more days.

33:30.310 --> 33:31.710
I killed the Prince of Luo

33:32.000 --> 33:33.530
for my own selfish reasons.

33:33.790 --> 33:35.160
I wanted to avenge Li Ce.

33:36.730 --> 33:38.440
But I can't let the current Biantang

33:38.440 --> 33:39.750
fall into a new crisis.

33:40.350 --> 33:42.750
The royal clan
is now circling like vultures.

33:42.750 --> 33:43.810
The moment I leave,

33:43.830 --> 33:45.020
those princes

33:45.240 --> 33:46.300
will form cliques.

33:46.640 --> 33:47.750
Li Ce helped me.

33:48.200 --> 33:49.330
I couldn't save him.

33:49.680 --> 33:51.810
But I want to protect Biantang for him.

33:52.880 --> 33:54.480
Only by becoming the Empress

33:54.550 --> 33:56.950
can I take charge
of the overall situation.

34:01.830 --> 34:02.640
I understand.

34:03.720 --> 34:05.790
I understand everything you said.

34:08.030 --> 34:09.440
But you haven't recovered yet,

34:09.440 --> 34:10.920
and you've been exhausted for days.

34:10.920 --> 34:12.380
Let me send you back first.

34:14.480 --> 34:15.070
No need.

34:16.190 --> 34:17.850
You should go to bed early too.

34:21.070 --> 34:21.760
Xing,

34:22.610 --> 34:23.989
no matter what you want to do,

34:23.989 --> 34:25.449
I will always wait for you.

34:26.320 --> 34:28.030
No matter whether it's
the Biantang royal clan surrounding us

34:28.030 --> 34:29.880
or the treacherous tides of change,

34:29.880 --> 34:31.810
nothing can tear us apart anymore.

34:32.280 --> 34:33.190
One day,

34:33.480 --> 34:35.280
we will surely fight side by side

34:35.710 --> 34:36.909
and walk hand in hand.

34:37.760 --> 34:38.630
Oh, no.

34:39.360 --> 34:40.840
It's all over now.

34:43.870 --> 34:46.010
[Three days later]

34:47.110 --> 34:49.440
The wedding of the Empress Dowager
and the late emperor...

34:49.440 --> 34:51.230
It's the first time
I've heard of something like this.

34:51.230 --> 34:52.150
Yes.

34:52.510 --> 34:55.360
We've never seen the style
of this wedding carriage.

34:55.360 --> 34:56.710
The star and moon lanterns on it

34:56.710 --> 34:59.110
don't seem to be commonly used
in Biantang.

35:11.480 --> 35:12.070
Xing,

35:13.000 --> 35:14.840
something happened
to the Ximeng delegation.

35:14.840 --> 35:16.970
I must depart for Ximeng immediately.

35:18.760 --> 35:21.490
You are staying in Biantang
to manage the crisis,

35:21.880 --> 35:25.320
and this will inevitably
draw the hostility of various forces.

35:25.320 --> 35:26.920
I'm leaving the 500 guards

35:27.590 --> 35:28.800
Li Ce promised me to you.

35:28.800 --> 35:30.400
They can help me protect you.

35:32.230 --> 35:34.950
This blood pigeon is raised
by the Queen of Lingyue.

35:34.950 --> 35:36.350
It recognizes its owner.

35:37.150 --> 35:38.320
If you need anything in the future,

35:38.320 --> 35:40.380
you can bring it to Ximeng and find me.

35:41.880 --> 35:43.630
The antidote Xiao Ran prepared for me

35:43.630 --> 35:46.360
can delay the onset
of the Blood on Snow in my body.

35:46.480 --> 35:48.280
You don't need to worry about me.

35:56.760 --> 35:57.480
Lady Chu,

35:57.880 --> 36:00.230
these are the Moon-star Lanterns
Young Master Zhuge

36:00.230 --> 36:01.830
specially prepared for you.

36:02.400 --> 36:03.720
Moon-star Lantern?

36:16.450 --> 36:17.160
Exactly.

36:20.480 --> 36:21.280
So beautiful.

36:21.670 --> 36:22.230
Yeah.

36:57.070 --> 36:57.840
Young Master,

36:57.840 --> 36:58.670
after crossing this mountain,

36:58.670 --> 37:00.870
we will be out of Biantang's territory.

37:05.260 --> 37:07.060
It's the direction of Tangjing.

37:07.280 --> 37:09.940
It's fireworks
for a celebration in the palace.

37:32.110 --> 37:33.190
From this day on,

37:33.550 --> 37:35.410
Biantang abolishes slave status

37:35.760 --> 37:37.480
and prohibits the slave trade.

37:37.480 --> 37:38.510
Who sent you here?

37:38.800 --> 37:40.600
Have you fallen in love with him?

37:41.650 --> 37:42.760
What exactly are you trying to say?

37:42.760 --> 37:45.200
I want to know King Ximeng's weakness.

37:45.230 --> 37:46.360
No!

37:46.360 --> 37:48.400
Whether your people can live

37:48.630 --> 37:49.630
depends entirely

37:49.880 --> 37:51.150
on you.

37:52.030 --> 37:54.070
Zhuge Yue is dying.

37:54.110 --> 37:54.880
Zhuge Yue!
